Investment accounts let you invest your money in various assets, potentially offering higher returns than savings accounts, but also carrying more risk.  We also have various savings accounts, offering different interest rates and access options.  Do you have a preference between higher risk, potentially higher reward investments, or lower risk, lower reward savings?
